  57:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/libDaisy/src/hid/switch.h ****     /** 
  58:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/libDaisy/src/hid/switch.h ****     Called at update_rate to debounce and handle timing for the switch.
  59:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/libDaisy/src/hid/switch.h ****     In order for events not to be missed, its important that the Edge/Pressed checks
  60:../VCOM-G1/GuitarPedal/libDaisy/src/hid/switch.h ****     be made at the same rate as the debounce function is being called.
